### Step 1: Create Account
POST http://localhost:5175/api/v1/accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "{{$guid}}@example.com",
  "username": "user{{$randomInt 1000 9999}}",
  "password": "Pass{{$randomInt 100000 999999}}!"
}

> {% client.global.set("accountId", response.body.id); %}


### Step 2: Create Title
POST http://localhost:5175/api/v1/titles
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "titleName": "Title {{$timestamp}}",
  "originalTitle": "Original {{$randomInt 100 999}}",
  "year": {{$randomInt 1990 2025}},
  "genre": "Drama",
  "runtimeMinutes": {{$randomInt 60 180}},
  "plot": "Generated plot {{$timestamp}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("titleId", response.body.id); %}


### Step 3: Create Rating (uses previous values)
POST http://localhost:5175/api/v1/accounts/{{accountId}}/ratings
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "titleId": "{{titleId}}",
  "score": {{$randomInt 1 10}},
  "comment": "Automated test comment {{$timestamp}}"
}

> {% client.global.set("ratingId", response.body.id); %}
